290
00:13:27,480 --> 00:13:28,930
♪This door♪

291
00:13:29,330 --> 00:13:34,080
♪Lets in the sky outside♪

292
00:13:34,560 --> 00:13:38,120
♪With a voice even lighter♪

293
00:13:38,120 --> 00:13:40,930
♪Than how you just greeted me♪

294
00:13:41,380 --> 00:13:42,750
♪I know now♪

295
00:13:43,080 --> 00:13:47,960
♪What the chill in my body means♪

296
00:13:48,310 --> 00:13:51,180
♪The moment salt hits the wound♪

297
00:13:51,380 --> 00:13:54,800
♪My heart still beats so naively♪

298
00:13:54,970 --> 00:13:57,960
♪To complete♪

299
00:13:58,420 --> 00:14:02,170
♪A joy that needs no brave pretense♪

300
00:14:02,310 --> 00:14:04,810
♪How cruel sincerity can be♪

301
00:14:04,950 --> 00:14:08,500
♪Like a door with no key♪

302
00:14:08,810 --> 00:14:11,130
♪Maybe you just passed by♪

303
00:14:11,130 --> 00:14:14,710
♪The tears in my eyes♪

304
00:14:15,420 --> 00:14:17,970
♪You looked like you had nothing to say♪

305
00:14:17,970 --> 00:14:19,710
♪Then got so good at being cold♪

306
00:14:19,710 --> 00:14:22,550
♪That's why a smile feels so precious♪

307
00:14:22,760 --> 00:14:24,850
♪Maybe you just passed by♪

308
00:14:25,000 --> 00:14:29,330
♪The tears burned into my heart♪

309
00:14:29,710 --> 00:14:32,000
♪Let's say silence was just for show♪

310
00:14:32,000 --> 00:14:36,670
♪Even if I've grown another year♪
